      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Visual works, including architecture, that are made of concrete, which is a hard, strong construction material comprising a mixture of sand, gravel, crushed rock that may be poured into molds. 

Visuelles Werk, einschließlich Werken der Architektur, hergestellt aus Beton, einem harten, starken Baumaterial, einer Mischung aus Sand, Kies und Gesteinsmehl, die in Formen gegossen werden kann.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
